    <item>
      <title>巴斯夫预计今年的收入将在大多数单位中提高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/basf-expects-earnings-to-improve-this-year-across-most-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴斯夫AG预计，随着其农业和营养单元的增长有助于抵消对陷入困境的汽车行业对化学和涂料的需求，今年的收入将略有上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/basf-expects-earnings-to-improve-this-year-across-most-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 06:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普拨号关税威胁时，新兴的亚洲市场发动了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/emerging-asia-markets-rattled-as-trump-dials-up-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，新兴的亚洲市场在全球股票风暴中席卷了，泰国和印尼股票摇摇欲坠，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统的最新关税威胁散发出风险资产卷起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/emerging-asia-markets-rattled-as-trump-dials-up-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 05:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言“所有必要的措施”，以应对新的美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统对中国进口的额外关税之后，中国威胁要对唐纳德·特朗普的贸易威胁进行反击，这增加了世界上最大的经济体之间紧张局势的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加密货币的恶化，比特币从历史高25％下降了25％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/bitcoin-down-25-from-all-time-high-as-crypto-selloff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）最新的关税威胁之后，投资者急于安全资产，这标志着世界上最受欢迎的特朗普交易之一的现实检查，这是一个急切的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/bitcoin-down-25-from-all-time-high-as-crypto-selloff-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普再次以更多关税威胁到中国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-says-us-will-impose-more-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他将对来自该国进口的进口征收10％的关税，这加剧了人们担心世界上两个最大经济体之间不断扩大的贸易战，他将额外征收10％的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-says-us-will-impose-more-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的新关税，港口集会：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统抢购危险的赌注，股票加强和财政部收益率降低了全球股票的抛售，而债务的收益率降低了，而国库券的收益却降低了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 22:35:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
